body:
With this pack installed, observers are altered to be more consistent with dispensers and, having a different front and back textures depending on the orientation. This pack also adds directional indicators to all these blocks to make their use more intuitive.

I have a different project that alters the dispenser and dropper instead, if you believe you would prefer that style, click the following link: [Consistent Sentries: Observer Style](https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/consistent-sentries-observer_style)

**Extra details**

- the current version of the pack is compatible with 1.21.9 to 26.1;
- the zip file can just be dragged and dropped in your "resourcepacks" folder, unzipping isn't required;
